-- China Rainstorm Halts Beijing-Baotou Rail Traffic, Xinhua Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-07-26T01:51:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-26/china-rainstorm-halts-beijing-baotou-rail-traffic-xinhua-says.html
A rainstorm flooded a section of the
railway linking Beijing and Baotou city in Inner Mongolia and
delayed 24 trains, the official Xinhua News Agency reported
today, citing railway authorities.  About 12,000 passengers have been stranded, Xinhua said,
citing an unidentified spokesman with the railway authorities.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
